 2023-03662023-04-21TC
ActInternational Bridges and Tunnels Act
SubjectAlteration of the Customs Facilities on the Canadian side of the Edmundston-Madawaska International Bridge
PrecisOrder approving the alteration of the customs facilities on the Canadian side of the EDMUNDSTON-MADAWASKA INTERNATIONAL BRIDGE in Edmundston, New Brunswick, in order to (1) improve efficiency; and (2) facilitate the movement of passenger traffic and road freight between Edmundston, New Brunswick and Madawaska, Maine.
